.RS 4
\fBQwtTextEngine\fP, \fBQwtText::setTextEngine\fP 
.RE
.PP
\fBWarning:\fP
.RS 4
Unfortunately the MathML renderer doesn't support rotating of texts\&. 
.RE
.PP

